<template>
  <v-navigation-drawer v-model="drawer">

      <v-row no-gutters>
        <v-column>
          <v-list>
            <v-list-item></v-list-item>

export default {
  name: "NavDrawer",
  props: {},
  data() {
    return {
      drawer: false,

  },
  methods: {
    openDrawer() {
      this.drawer = !this.drawer;
    },
  },
};
</script>
